OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,FJersey and Guernsey must not allow
OL,7,Fmedicinal cannabis to become a widely
OL,8,Favailable, commercial product, if they
OL,9,Fchoose to relax drug laws further,
OL,10,Faccording to one American health
OL,11,Fexpert.
OL,13,FDr Lynn Silver, a senior advisor for
OL,14,Fthe Public Health Institute, says
OL,15,Fcertain states in the USA are seeing
OL,16,Fincreased levels of addiction among
OL,17,Fthose who are prescribed medicinal
OL,18,Fcannabis inappropriately.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,FThe personal use of cannabis for
OL,7,Fmedicinal purposes is legal in 40 US
OL,8,Fstates and Dr Silver says while
OL,9,Fdecriminalising it is "very positive",
OL,10,Fshe argues it is putting a large
OL,11,Fnumber of users at risk.
OL,13,FThis is mainly due to incorrect
OL,14,Fadvertising of the what the substance
OL,15,Fshould be prescribed for and a lack of
OL,16,Fknowledge among doctors about how it
OL,17,Fshould be prescribed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,FDr Silver told ITV News: "We see
OL,7,Finsane promotion of marijuana use for
OL,8,Fa wide array of clinical conditions
OL,9,Ffor which it's not effective and may
OL,10,Feven be harmful, for example,
OL,11,Fdepression.
OL,13,F"You go in (to the doctor's) and you
OL,14,Fsee folders and flyers and this will
OL,15,Ffix what ails you, this is a safe
OL,16,Fwellness product."
OL,26,@uD@LpmuD@\pn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,FShe added that the drug is even being
OL,7,Fmarketed as a routine painkiller and
OL,8,Fthat's because most doctors are not
OL,9,Ffamiliar enough with how they should
OL,10,Fprescribe the drug.
OL,12,FShe added some patients are being
OL,13,Fgiven "highly potent" doses up to ten
OL,14,Ftimes higher than the recommended
OL,15,Famount for their specific condition.
OL,17,FDr Silver says this can "facilitate"
OL,18,Faddiction.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,FResponding to questions about how
OL,7,FJersey could avoid this problem if it
OL,8,Fwere to relax laws around cannabis
OL,9,Fuse, Dr Silver said the island's
OL,10,Fgovernment should avoid copying the
OL,11,FStates.
OL,13,FShe said: "When you devise your policy
OL,14,Ffor Jersey, be very careful.
OL,16,F"I would strongly discourage allowing
OL,17,Fthe emergence of any kind of for
OL,18,Fprofit kind of cannabis industry."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,FThis conversation comes after a UK
OL,7,Fcoroner ruled that medicinal cannabis
OL,8,F- prescribed legally - had contributed
OL,9,Fto the death of Oliver Robinson. He
OL,10,Ftook his own life after being told to
OL,11,Ftake a high dose by a private clinic,
OL,12,Fdespite a history of mental illness.
OL,14,FThe number of prescriptions for
OL,15,Fmedicinal cannabis in Jersey more than
OL,16,Fdoubled between 2022 and 2024, with
OL,17,Fover 53,000 being handed out.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,FAnd in 2025, more than 1 in 5
OL,7,Fadmissions to the hospital's acute
OL,8,Fadult mental health ward were linked
OL,9,Fto cannabis - both that which was
OL,10,Fprescribed or from other sources.
OL,12,FIt is a similar picture in Guernsey
OL,13,Ftoo, where 18% of admissions to the
OL,14,FAdult Mental Health Service were
OL,15,Flinked to, or caused by, cannabis use.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,FDr Kirstie Ross, a medic specialising
OL,7,Fin medicinal cannabis in Jersey, says
OL,8,Fthere are some conditions for which
OL,9,Fthe drug is suitable and can be
OL,10,Fbeneficial, including insomnia,
OL,11,Fanxiety, chronic pain and certain
OL,12,Fcomplications arising from cancer
OL,13,Ftreatment.
OL,15,FDr Ross adds that overdosing can cause
OL,16,Fschizophrenia and bi-polar disorder.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,FHowever, Dr Ross says: "The sad thing
OL,7,Fis that if it's prescribed and managed
OL,8,Fproperly, that risk goes away and you
OL,9,Fshould not be prescribing it to people
OL,10,Fwith schizophrenia or bipolar but for
OL,11,Fpeople with depression, that's
OL,12,Fsomething that really needs to be
OL,13,Fclosely monitored."
OL,15,FShe says regular communication between
OL,16,Fcannabis clinics and other care
OL,17,Fproviders can help make treatment
OL,18,Fsafer.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,FDr Ross also told ITV News that
OL,7,Fillegal cannabis use is completely
OL,8,Fsupplied by an on-island illegal
OL,9,Fcannabis market and wants the next
OL,10,FGovernment to cap the amounts clinics
OL,11,Fcan prescribe to tackle crime.
OL,13,F"As clinics, it is our responsibility
OL,14,Fto make sure that the amounts we are
OL,15,Fprescribing are in line with
OL,16,Frecommendations and are proportional
OL,17,Fand I think that's obviously happening
OL,18,Fsomewhere because it's getting to the
OL,19,Fmarket in the illegal sense.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779898263
OL,3,CChannel Islands must learn from US
OL,4,Cmistakes on medicinal cannabis
OL,6,F"So if the Government were to put caps
OL,7,Fon amounts that were allowed to be
OL,8,Fprescribed, that would very quickly
OL,9,Fdeal with that illegal market as a
OL,10,Fproblem."
OL,12,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,13,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,14,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,15,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,16,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,17,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,18,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,19,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,20,FThursday...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
